        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2447318919" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3193013659161168073">Great popular history of the country as it falls into civil war, including lots of good vignettes and tracing major social movements and controversies that have been all but forgotten due to the conflagration that followed.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


